headline: Why Is Datadog (DDOG) Stock Soaring Today
summary: Shares of cloud monitoring platform Datadog (NASDAQ:DDOG) jumped 7.3% in the afternoon session after Stifel upgraded the stock from a "Hold" to a "Buy," citing expectations for a strong fourth-quarter performance.
